{
  "stem": "3855.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I want to continue where we stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these fellows would get stone drunk, and ride on their horses through the town, and beat up anybody that wasn't fast enough to pull the merchandise back into their little stores.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They usually slept behind the store and closed these heavy wooden doors that they had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in a small town called Rozniatow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- R-O-Z with a certain accent N-I-A-T-O-W.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was near Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And so that is also an illustration of the, the mindset and the mind of these people that made these Jewish storekeepers-- who, by no means, were affluent-- as the victim of their aggressive behavior that came through when they were drunk.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a cry that if-- let us say, if, for some reason or other, a Jew drove a car through the town and hit a Gentile child or something like that, the crime-- Polish word, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Jew killed a Polish man, a Pollack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the same thing would happen, regardless of whether they were drunk or not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Well, my uncle was in a different sphere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle was the revered physician in town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Already, police officials brought their girlfriends to him for abortions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was very, very needed and very revered in this town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was a wonderful physician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was strictly in the company of the intelligentsia and the industrialists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So really, I guess we just chalked it up to what is called, [GERMAN], which is [POLISH], which is people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the German-- Austrian word for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it occurred while I was there, during those almost three months that I was there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this would happen invariably on those days where there was what is called, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
